ime":"2020-11-22T06:39:39.000Z","msg":"當年個垃圾師傅淨係叫找望遠d,&nbsp;無教我睇A柱同望鏡對線.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n自己摸返黎,&nbsp;比佢扼多幾堂錢,&nbsp;屌佢老母."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:57:45.000Z","msg":"嘩 咁樣巴打pass到都有實力<br />\n想當年我左西右西俾師傅屌到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5f866b6de8279f6c83557f72f2be2ac55da52e","tid":2295984,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"35563301e0f050d4b016355f6c6b658ced16fa8a","tid":2295984,"uid":77813,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32f7c8c39b764c61d402c3c33ae1b7b5c265ad63","tid":2295984,"uid":126731,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"d907f95f78a02dfd731d64e1196fa69bcbf5a8e9","tid":2295984,"uid":77813,"like":59,"dislike":7,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:36:59.000Z","msg":"望鏡睇窗角學車時無教？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T06:39:39.000Z","msg":"當年個垃圾師傅淨係叫找望遠d,&nbsp;無教我睇A柱同望鏡對線.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n自己摸返黎,&nbsp;比佢扼多幾堂錢,&nbsp;屌佢老母."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:57:45.000Z","msg":"嘩 咁樣巴打pass到都有實力<br />\n想當年我左西右西俾師傅屌到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T08:12:06.000Z","msg":"講起就嬲,&nbsp;條仆街遲到早退,&nbsp;次次我黎到就去WC,&nbsp;學到一半就話返去接學生佢渣返.&nbsp;又話我廢鳩屌整壞佢個極力子.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n除左佢架死人車多cheat&nbsp;泊位調頭1&nbsp;take,&nbsp;考第一次肥過死車無望盲點(佢條撚樣無教).&nbsp;其他考試都似樣.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n之後轉第2個師傅一點就知點望盲點(做戲要做捉),&nbsp;補4堂練熟條線就pass左.&nbsp;最後一堂仲比我渣龍翔道返九龍塘,&nbsp;又教過過窄位.&nbsp;比埋師傅手冊我睇點過死車.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n好似停車熄匙, 拉手制, 入前/後波(睇地形),&nbsp;我識人因為個考官裝彈官扮落車先再返手裝考生,&nbsp;所以埋尾都有做,&nbsp;而個考官又真係玩呢招.&nbsp;我就知自己PASS硬&nbsp;(中途肥左你就無必要臨尾陰你).<br />\n<br />\n同埋考車好多汁生位,&nbsp;燈位前面塞車你過唔過埋個D,&nbsp;唔可以唔用自己個腦去諗同反應,&nbsp;又唔可以乜都靠晒師傅,&nbsp;因為考完試就無師傅,&nbsp;香港D師傅都鐘意留手,&nbsp;你唔遇到唔同你講.&nbsp;要靠自己觀察同睇人點渣,&nbsp;諗點解再跟住學."},{"pid":"9a09c860f3614ebae0872d9d52fda1d7cdfbd984","tid":2295984,"uid":357612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T21:22:59.000Z","msg":"認真,望遠d,靠感覺"},{"pid":"66f3b9b6889c308be9d038125ad5b3ec2b86867b","tid":2295984,"uid":90060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T22:14:54.000Z","msg":"試過入停車場簽名同聽聲停，就會學得識"},{"pid":"62f05b733b8d805d361c677dfde8b8e42d9698dc","tid":2295984,"uid":373220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T22:22:51.000Z","msg":"你越望住條線就越左右搖擺<br />\n要望遠<br />\n眼尾得閒瞄一眼就得"},{"pid":"d1e3e53bbf401ed9557ba7f2259945ae0369e6df","tid":2295984,"uid":60279,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T23:11:31.000Z","msg":"洗撚咩<br />\n望遠d就會自然係中間<br />\n下下focus係車頭 你永遠都覺得唔正中 不停修正"},{"pid":"1efd152fef4a2ffe6c2be03b3b62bfb4b811ba4c","tid":2295984,"uid":5650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T23:24:19.000Z","msg":"望遠 望鏡"},{"pid":"2dabf4c4d306a2375ebe08fbee013d77fc7f40ef","tid":2295984,"uid":67353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T00:53:21.000Z","msg":"我係靠擋風玻璃右下角個位係唔係係條線上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99fd975e8b2a0e3fc4e96d2028e46d5a68b242a7","tid":2295984,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dabf4c4d306a2375ebe08fbee013d77fc7f40ef","tid":2295984,"uid":67353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T00:53:21.000Z","msg":"我係靠擋風玻璃右下角個位係唔係係條線上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T00:55:40.000Z","msg":"呢招一樣唔會正中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d578d49e4326fe8b663e51fdb3261ed77aa1991","tid":2295984,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T00:55:42.000Z","msg":"Subaru EyeSight<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" cla